[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA fuzzing session using the `TestFuzzCodecs` harness against FreeRDP’s codec [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibrary triggered an AddressSanitizer-detected segmentation fault. The crash is a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwrite to an invalid memory address in the function `rfx_process_message_metadata` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39min `libfreerdp/codec/rfx.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, invoked via `rfx_process_message` and ultimately [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrough the `TestFreeRDPCodecRemoteFX` entry point in the fuzzer harness. [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAddressSanitizer classified the error as a wild-address write [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSEGV[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The issue was observed when running the `TestFuzzCodecs` binary under libFuzzer [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith AddressSanitizer enabled. After loading the seed corpus and running a test [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcase [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m times, the codec logged multiple errors from the clear codec [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`clear_decompress_residual_data` failures[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m before aborting on a memory write [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mviolation.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The sanitizer output reports:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Error Type: SEGV on unknown address [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwild-addr-write[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Faulting Location:  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • `rfx_process_message_metadata` at `libfreerdp/codec/rfx.[0m[1;92mc:734:26[0m[39m`  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • Called by `rfx_process_message` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`rfx.[0m[1;92mc:1320:10[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • Rooted in the fuzz test function `TestFreeRDPCodecRemoteFX` in [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TestFuzzCodecs.c`.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The vulnerability type is memory corruption due to an out-of-bounds or otherwise [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvalid write.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Important observations:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Prior clear-codec errors indicate that malformed input was already stressing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe codec’s boundary checks.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The crash occurs in the RemoteFX [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`rfx`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m codec metadata-processing logic.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The fuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`TestFuzzCodecs.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m serves as the entry point for feeding [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marbitrary input into the codec; it is not the root cause but reproduces the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfailure.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- To gain a holistic view of the issue, investigation should focus on:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `rfx_process_message_metadata` and related metadata parsing routines in [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`libfreerdp/codec/rfx.c`.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. The higher-level `rfx_process_message` function to see how metadata frames are[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdispatched.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. The fuzzer harness code in `libfreerdp/codec/test/TestFuzzCodecs.c`, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparticularly the `TestFreeRDPCodecRemoteFX` function, to understand buffer setup [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand how input is passed into the codec.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Any data-structure definitions or buffer-size checks around RemoteFX packet [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandling in the codec library.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo speculation on root cause or fixes is provided in this report; the focus is [0m     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m728[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT32[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, magic[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[39m* magic [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m0xCACCACCA[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [32m0x%08"[0m[39m PRIX32 [0m[32m""[0m[39m, magic[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m732[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn FALSE;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m733[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m734[0m[39m:    [0m[39m*[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mmetadataBlock = metadataData;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m735[0m[39m:    [0m[39mreturn TRUE;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibfreerdp/codec/rfx.[0m[1;92mc:1314[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1323[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1314[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase WBT_EXTENSION:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1315[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mok = [0m[1;35mrfx_process_message_tileset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext, message, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubStream,[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1316[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m                                 [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m&context->expectedDataBlockType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1317[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mbreak;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1318[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1319[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mcase WBT_METADATA:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1320[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mok = [0m[1;35mrfx_process_message_metadata[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext, message,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubStream,[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1321[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m                                 [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m&context->expectedDataBlockType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1322[0m[39m:   [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mbreak;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1323[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `rfx_process_message_metadata`, the code unconditionally does:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       *[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mmetadataBlock = metadataData;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     where `metadataBlock` is initialized to the address of the function [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`explicit_bzero`, and `metadataData` is always zero.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This leads to an invalid write [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwild write[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m into code space, triggering the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAddressSanitizer crash.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Neither `metadataBlock` nor `metadataData` is ever set to a valid target or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mused meaningfully elsewhere in the codec, indicating that metadata handling is [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munimplemented or placeholder.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Preservation of Existing Functionality[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The patch strictly confines itself to the metadata-processing path [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`rfx_process_message_metadata` in `rfx.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All other RemoteFX block types [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtileset, palettes, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and control flow [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mmagic‐number check, expected‐block‐type enforcement[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remain unchanged.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer harness, test code, and any higher‐level RemoteFX logic are [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muntouched.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Proposed Fix[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Remove the unsafe write[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Delete the line:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          *[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mmetadataBlock = metadataData;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This immediately eliminates the wild-address write.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Simplify metadata handling to a no-op[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - After validating `*pExpectedBlockType` and the magic number, simply return [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTRUE.[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Optionally reset the expected block type if needed; however, the calling [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop will advance and free the substream, so no further action is required.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. Remove/cleanup unused globals[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Remove the global variables `metadataBlock` and `metadataData` from [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`rfx.c`:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          UINT64 metadataBlock = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m&explicit_bzero;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          UINT64 metadataData = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This avoids dead‐code and compiler warnings.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   D. Document unsupported metadata[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - In the body of `rfx_process_message_metadata`, add a comment explaining [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat metadata blocks are currently unsupported and are safely skipped.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Implementation Steps[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. In `libfreerdp/codec/rfx.c`, find the function `rfx_process_message_metadata`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m709[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Remove or comment out the line at [0m[1;36m734[0m[39m:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         *[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mmetadataBlock = metadataData;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Ensure that immediately after the magic‐number check [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m729[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m733[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction does:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return TRUE;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpreserving existing error‐checks for unexpected block type and invalid [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmagic[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Remove the two global declarations at lines [0m[1;36m142[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`metadataBlock`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m179[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`metadataData`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Recompile and run the `TestFuzzCodecs` harness under AddressSanitizer to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mverify that the wild write no longer occurs and that metadata blocks are simply [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mskipped.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Run existing codec tests to confirm no regressions in tile, palette, or other[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mblock processing.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Eliminates the root‐cause invalid write without touching harness or test code.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Keeps existing RemoteFX parsing logic intact for all other block types.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Metadata was clearly unimplemented/placeholder code; harmlessly skipping [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmetadata preserves stability.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No side effects on tile, end‐of‐frame, or clear‐codec paths.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Cleaner code by removing unused globals.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential Side‐Effects & Mitigation[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Side‐Effect: metadata in RemoteFX messages will be ignored. If metadata [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msupport is required in the future, a full implementation must be provided.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: log a debug‐level message in `rfx_process_message_metadata` noting[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat metadata was skipped, so maintainers know why it’s a no‐op.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. References[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No external dependencies are modified.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar safe‐skip approach is used elsewhere in the codebase when encountering[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munsupported block types [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., palette extensions[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
